### Health
GET {{baseUrlIAManager}}/health

### Retrieve de resource list (tables) from MCP
POST {{baseUrlMCP}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "resources/list",
  "params": {},
  "id": 1
}

### Retrieve data from gig_db via assistant
###
POST {{baseUrlIAManager}}/prompt
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "What are the available tables in the database?"
}

### Match workers based on criteria
POST {{baseUrlIAManager}}/match-workers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "skills": ["python", "C++", "Java", "PHP"],
  "gigDate": "<yyyy-mm-dd>",
  "latitude": 51.5,
  "longitude": 0.0,
  "radius": 30,
  "limit": 20,
  "hourlyRate": 50,
  "required": ["mac"]
}

### Get recommendation
POST {{baseUrlIAManager}}/recommendations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "prompt": "Give me suggestions about my user profile."
}

